title: Previews (307 & 307 Adult) (April 2014)
description:
Previews (307 & 307 Adult) (April 2014) 

THIS MONTH'S COVER ART: New projects from DC and Dark Horse!

THIS MONTH'S THEME: Movie Blockbusters!

Since 1988, PREVIEWS has been your ultimate source for all of the comics and merchandise to be available from your local comic book shop... revealed up to two months in advance! Hundreds of comics and graphic novels from the best comic publishers; the coolest pop-culture merchandise on Earth; plus PREVIEWS exclusive items available nowhere else! Now more than ever, PREVIEWS is here to show the tales, toys and treasures in your future! This April issue features items scheduled to ship in June 2014 and beyond.
